  <title>Add a stock</title>
  
  <p>
	To add a stock, click on <gui>Preferences</gui>, select the <gui>Stocks</gui> tab,
	then enter the stocks symbol in the textbox and click the <gui>Add</gui> button.
  </p>

  <note style="tip">
    <p>
      You can find the stock symbol for a company 
      at <link href="http://finance.yahoo.com/">Yahoo Finance</link>.
    </p>
    <p>
      For example,
      <code>AMD.DE</code> is the symbol for <em>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. (Equity-XETRA)</em>,
      <code>INTC</code> is the symbol for <em>Intel Corporation (Equity-NASDAQ)</em>.
    </p>
  </note>

